Ranger Help for: radvance
=========================

SYNTAX:      radvance <level|guild|str|dex|con|int|wis|chr>
USAGE:       Any wilderness area.

SUMMARY:
Advance your stats or game level, or review automatic Ranger guild progress,
from anywhere in the wilderness. You do not need to return to the lodge.

  radvance level     Advance your game level (costs experience)
  radvance guild     Show combat-earned Ranger XP progress
  radvance str       Raise your strength
  radvance dex       Raise your dexterity
  radvance con       Raise your constitution
  radvance int       Raise your intelligence
  radvance wis       Raise your wisdom
  radvance chr       Raise your charisma

REQUIREMENTS:
- Must be in the wilderness (not city, indoors, or dock)
- Terrains and enemy species must be set before guild level 2
- Guild level cannot exceed your game level
- Use 'rcost' to check character costs and Ranger XP

